snippet.title: Renewable Energy is Here 🍃| Power Network Tycoon
snippet.description:
A major update has just been released to add Renewable Energy to Power Network Tycoon. You can now power your island with Solar Panels, Wind Turbines and Grid Batteries. New challenges have been added with managing Grid Inertia and the unpredictable weather for your power sources. Check it out today!

★ Buy the Game! ★
